    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Cn</abbr><ex>aeus</ex></expan> Vettius Globulus <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>d<supplied reason="lost">is</supplied>signat</abbr><ex>or</ex></expan> Caesaru<supplied reason="lost">m e</supplied>t <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">m</supplied>ag</abbr><ex>ister</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>H</abbr><ex>erculis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>V</abbr><ex>ictoris</ex></expan> et se<supplied reason="lost">vir <expan><abbr>August</abbr><ex>alis</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf dem Block steht eine Statue; Block und Statue gehören allerdings nicht zusammen. (B): Z. 2: Pala, AE 1976: d[issi]gnat(or) Caesaru[m ---]t; Z. 3 von Pala nicht gelesen; AE 1976: [--- v]igilu(m) et st[---] oder se[---]. Y: Die beiden Herrscher sind wohl Marc Aurel/Verus, Marc Aurel/ Commodus oder Septimius Severus/Caracalla.</p>
            </div>
